OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cdescending on Cardiff
OL,6,FThousands of farmers on Wednesday, in
OL,7,Fthe biggest protest seen so far
OL,8,Fagainst the Welsh government's future
OL,9,Fsubsidy plans.
OL,11,FUp to 100 tractors are expected to
OL,12,Ftravel in convoy to the capital from
OL,13,FBrecon, and will join from around the
OL,14,Fcountry.
OL,16,FMany are angry at the Welsh
OL,17,Fgovernment's Sustainable Farming
OL,18,FScheme until March 7.
