OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cdescending on Cardiff
OL,6,FThe current proposals would see
OL,7,Ffarmers required to ensure 10% of
OL,8,Ftheir land is woodland, with a further
OL,9,F10% earmarked for habitat, in order to
OL,10,Fbe eligible for government subsidies.
OL,12,FThe scheme is supported by
OL,13,Forganisations such as Coed Cadw (the
OL,14,FWoodlands Trust in Wales) and the
OL,15,FWildlife Trust and is part of .
