OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cdescending on Cardiff
OL,6,FA recent economic impact assessment
OL,7,Fcommissioned by the Welsh Government
OL,8,Ffound that the scheme could see a
OL,9,F10.8% reduction in livestock numbers
OL,10,Fand an 11% drop in labour numbers in
OL,11,Fthe sector, equivalent to 5,500 jobs.
OL,13,FIts publication led to across rural
OL,14,FWales which have slowly escalated.
