OL,6,FIn Wrexham, one man was arrested for
OL,7,Fcriminal damage when tractors
OL,8,Fblockaded the office of Rural Affairs
OL,9,FMinister Lesley Griffiths, while the
OL,10,Ffirst minister was heckled by
OL,11,Fprotestors on a visit to a college in
OL,12,FRhyl, causing the building to be
OL,13,Flocked down.
