OL,16,Ffor the Welsh Labour government, the
OL,17,FPrime Minister last week, telling a
OL,18,Fsmall crowd of farmers outside the
OL,19,FWelsh Conservative Party Conference in
OL,20,FLlandudno that he had their backs.
