OL,3,CWhy thousands of farmers are
OL,4,Cdescending on Cardiff
OL,6,FThe minister responsible for
OL,7,Fagricultural policy, Lesley Griffiths,
OL,8,Ftold ITV News she was "sad" her
OL,9,Frelationship with farmers had
OL,10,Fdeteriorated, but insisted the
OL,11,Fgovernment was listening to them.
OL,13,FShe said changes would be made to the
OL,14,Fscheme but refused to give details.
OL,16,FBut that concession seems unlikely to
OL,17,Fdissuade the thousands travelling from
OL,18,Fevery corner of Wales to the capital
OL,19,Fin tractors and buses. It could be the
OL,20,Fbiggest protest outside the Senedd in
OL,21,Fits history.
